  <div id="about_lead">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Scott Nedderman (<%= link_to "@scottned", "http://www.twitter.com/scottned"%>) and Chris Beck (<%= link_to "@christopherbeck", "http://www.twitter.com/christopherbeck"%>) merged their web consulting firms together in 2007, creating Netphase (<%= link_to "@netphase", "http://www.twitter.com/netphase"%>) as a two-man Ruby on Rails development shop based in Charlotte, NC. Today, they are fortunate enough to work with an excellent team of software engineers, graphic designers, systems architects, and strategy specialists to provide excellent service and results for any sized or type of technology project.</p>
    <p>Netphase is constantly searching for dedicated self-starters who have a passion for their craft. If you are creative, dependable, professional, and simply outstanding at what you do, <%= link_to "we want to hear from you", "mailto:jobs@netphase.com" %>.</p>
