<div id="about">
  <div class="grid_9 alpha line">
    <div class="line_right left box">
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>We are a technology consulting firm that provides web, mobile and infrastructure development and strategy to medium to large organizations.</p>
      <p>We prefer technologies that balance application scalability with rapid development, but assess each project individually to determine the right tools and resources for the job. The technologies and processes we employ allow us to deliver better solutions with fewer resources in less time, providing significant ROI.</p>  
      <p>Our people have been providing consulting services for everyone from top-5 financial institutions to fast-paced Silicon Valley start-ups for almost 15 years. We understand what it takes to deliver successful projects to production.</p>
      <p><%= link_to "Contact us today", contact_us_path %> to schedule a free initial consultation. You will be glad you did.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right box">
     <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
      <p>We focus our approach on three things:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Understanding all of your organization's goals for the project before we begin.</li>
        <li>Agreement on the approach that both meets those goals and provides opportunities that were previously not considered.</li>
        <li>Delivering excellence and standing behind our work.</li>
      </ol>
      <p>We strive to provide the right solution for any project, not just the flavor-of-the-month hot technology. That being said, we have a culture of learning at Netphase, and we place great emphasis on making sure that our team-members stay ahead of the curve.</p>
      <p>We honor efficiency, honesty, elegance, simplicity, and effectiveness as team-member traits. We offer the same to our clients.</p>
    </div>
    
